  - 'C-b c' parses to expected KeybindSequence (insta snapshot)
  - 'M-S-Tab' parses with both modifiers
  - feed() sequences across multiple chords resolve correctly
  - ambiguous prefixes ('C-b' alone, 'C-b c', 'C-b d') don't confuse the
